title: Mahjong Deluxe 2 v1.0.7
description:
Mahjong Deluxe 2 takes our super popular mahjong solitaire game and brings it into a whole new world. The tiles are placed on 3D planes and you rotate around the structures to find the matching tiles. 

It comes with 84 puzzle layouts and all puzzles are laid out with random tile orders so you can play them many times. Relax and enjoy this beautiful game today!

Features:

â˜… 84 different puzzle layouts with a different puzzle each time.
â˜… All tiles are always open. If you can touch it you can select it.
â˜… New point and star system designed to help keep you focused.
â˜… Great background music and sounds.

What's New:

Changed match time from 25 to 30 seconds per match.
If you run out of time it makes a sound and you get 0 points for that match but can keep playing and get points on the rest of the matches.
Fixed navigation where sometimes going straight up would not work.
Added in Flurry analytics.
Added in new localized descriptions.
We fixed "level competed" to "level completed" at the end for each completed level.
